PEOPLE ex rel. ROSEBORN, Appellant, v. JEROLOMAN, Justice, et al., Respondents. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. May 10, 1894.) Action by the People on relation of Harry W. Roseborn against John J. Jeroloman, justice, and others.

Argued before DALY, C. J., and BOOKSTAVER and PRYOR, JJ.

J. C. Roseborn, for appellant. Edwin A. Pratt, for respondents.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with costs.
